"G" located his business next to us because we have a lot of traffic. It is unfair and unethical to target us for this situation. Our store has been here for over 30 years dealing with the parking as best we can, while "G" has only recently located here. We have never publicly complained about anyone or blocked anyone from parking period; but now our customers are being blocked from parking in violation of our lease; everyday by "G" and his staff. There is absolutely no credibility to any of "G"'s claims regarding our booths or our prices. This is a simple case a man who did not properly investigate his location or negotiate his lease. The statement regarding handicap parking is also not true. I hope that Google will delete "G"'s post; but in the mean time; we vigorously regret that "G" has stooped so low as to put his mean and untruthful comments in a Google review and also that we have no other option than to vigorously refute these lies.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Had a horrible experience here with the night staff this past Saturday. Have been trying to reach an actual manager since but no luck. Not sure who to file a complaint with because they would not give their names. I enjoyed my first hour. A young lady came to check tickets and mine had just expired. I go to the counter to renew but the price is now $22 not the initial $15 I paid. I inquired about it and apparently hadn't been charged for one side on my first hour. Cool, I go to hand the clerk my card and he instead tells me to have a nice night?? I was very confused and at first thought it was a joke so I asked if he was serious. His response is yes I am refusing your service you need to leave now. Never once looking me in the face. So I ask what his name is and he tells me he doesn't have to tell me his name. Then I ask for the managers name and he said he is the manager. Before I could say anything else the young lady working with him tells me I'm making it worse and to get out. She also said that she would not let me in on her shift. Again, why all of that happened I'm completely dumbfounded. I drove over an hour to this place, and to be treated that nasty by staff with no explanation was probably one of the worst experiences I've ever had anywhere. If a manager sees this, please work with your night staff. I didn't cause problems for anyone. Only inquired about the price discrepancy and that was enough to be refused service. Not everyone lives in that area and it was personally only my 2nd time there.

UPDATE: reached out to management and they have turned this situation around. Thank you to Kim for reaching out to me and extending your hospitality to return back to the store! I really appreciate you taking the time like a good manager does to make a wrong, right!

Gecen Cumartesi gece personeli ile burada korkunc bir deneyim yasadim. O zamandan beri gercek bir yoneticiye ulasmaya calisiyorum ama sans yok. Let me start off by saying I have NEVER left a negative review about any establishment in
my life before this moment... but this, I guess, will be my first.
I bought a HydroMax pump from this store that was $160.00 (after taxes). When I got home I realirealized that I had gotten the wrong size (too small) and there was no way that I could used it... so I just left it in the box.
I called the store and told the assistant manager that I had just purchased it, that it was $160.00, that I still have the receipt, that it's still in the box, that it's literally untouched, and that I didn't even want my money back.
All I wanted was to exchange it for the correct item.
She said:
"Its your job as the customer to make sure you leave with the right item. Even though our staff member helped you select it, it's your responsibility in the end."
.
Nothing else.
Basically a cold, hard wall is all I got for feedback.
So...
I just spent $160.00 for something I can't use, and they wont let me exchange for another size... even though I have the receipt, the box was unopened, and I asked to swap it RIGHT AFTER I purchased it.
I shouldn't have went there. I should have went to my usual store (especially after reading some of the reviews), but I thought I'd give them a try and draw my own conclusion.
That... was... a mistake...
The above statement is my rewiew, so I'm sure my conclusion is clear.
I will never go back.
.
There's a review about another guy that spend over $100, walked out the front door to the sidewalk, realized he bought the wrong thing, and walked back in to exchange it (LITERALLY 30 SECONDS AFTER HE PURCHASED IT) and they told him no as well.
Don't go here.
Their customer service is every bit as bad as the reviews say it is on Yelp.

Herhangi bir kurulus hakkinda ASLA olumsuz bir inceleme birakmadigimi soyleyerek baslayayim.
bu andan onceki hayatim... ama bu, sanirim, benim ilkim olacak.
Bu magazadan 160,00 $'a (vergiler sonrasi) bir HydroMax pompasi satin aldim. Eve geldigimde yanlis beden aldigimi (cok kucuk) fark ettim ve kullanmamin hicbir yolu yoktu... bu yuzden kutuya biraktim.
Magazayi aradim ve mudur yardimcisina urunu yeni aldigimi, 160,00 TL oldugunu, faturasinin hala bende oldugunu, kutunun icinde oldugunu, kelimenin tam anlamiyla dokunulmamis oldugunu ve parami bile istemedigimi soyledim. geri.
Tek istedigim dogru urunle degistirmekti.
dedi ki:
"Musteri olarak dogru urunle ayrilmanizi saglamak sizin goreviniz. Personelimiz urunu secmenize yardimci olsa da, sonucta bu sizin sorumlulugunuzdur."
.
Baska hicbir sey.
Temelde soguk, sert bir duvar, geri bildirim icin sahip oldugum tek sey.
Bu yuzden...
Az once kullanamayacagim bir sey icin 160,00 dolar harcadim ve baska bir bedenle degistirmeme izin vermiyorlar... faturasi oldugu halde kutusu acilmamisti ve satin aldiktan HEMEN SONRA degistirmek istedim.
Oraya gitmemeliydim. Her zamanki magazama gitmeliydim (ozellikle bazi incelemeleri okuduktan sonra), ama onlari bir deneyip kendi sonucumu cikaracagimi dusundum.
O bir hataydi...
Yukaridaki ifade benim incelememdir, bu yuzden sonucumun acik oldugundan eminim.
Asla geri donmeyecegim.
.
100 dolardan fazla harcayan, on kapidan kaldirima cikan, yanlis bir sey aldigini fark eden ve onu degistirmek icin geri donen (GERCEKTEN 30 SANIYE SONRA) baska bir adam hakkinda bir inceleme var ve ona da hayir dediler .
buraya gitme

featured_reviews.review_id:
The shining 5-star reviews you see here are not from actual customers.
I bought a Bliss Shaft Rider from this merchant.  The box was sealed so there was no way for me to test the device before I purchased it.
I got home, charged it and pushed the power button...nothing.

They sold me a broken (or defective) toy for $87.59. I took it back the next day, well within 24 hours after purchase. Their website states they will take returns of defective products if you contact them within 24 hours. The clerk refused to accept the return stating "We don't accept returns, ever." When I pushed he said I would have to speak to the owners and they are unavailable and he has no idea when they will be available.
Before leaving I had the clerk test the device himself. He confirmed it is defective and still refused to accept the return.

I contacted them through their website, per the instructions on the website,  a couple hours after I purchased the defective device and still have not heard back from them over 2 weeks later.

Take my advice, avoid this place.  Their markup is at least 800%,  Amazon has better quality devices, better selection and waaaay better prices.

********Response to Owner**********
The receipt was not the issue as I had and still have my receipt. I showed it to the clerk, he had no interest in it.
I am not convinced you never received an email from me and doesn't it just feel gross to respond to a review/complaint by lying about it so that you can hold on to $87.00? I mean, seriously? Your integrity is worth less than $87.00?
As you already know, it is the policy of your store to refuse to refund, exchange or in any other manner rectify any situation such as this which would require you to return funds to a customer.

You are running a shady operation, just own that. Think of how great it will feel to be able to just be yourself and not need to lie to the people who read this review.

Burada gordugunuz parlak 5 yildizli incelemeler gercek musterilerden degildir.
Bu tuccardan bir Bliss Shaft Rider satin aldim. Kutu muhurlu oldugundan, satin almadan once cihazi test etmemin bir yolu yoktu.
Eve geldim, sarj ettim ve guc dugmesine bastim...hicbir sey olmadi.

Bana kirik (veya kusurlu) bir oyuncagi 87,59 dolara sattilar. Ertesi gun, satin aldiktan 24 saat sonra geri goturdum. Web sitelerinde 24 saat icinde iletisime gecmeniz halinde arizali urunleri iade edecekleri belirtiliyor. Gorevli "Asla iade kabul etmiyoruz" diyerek iadeyi kabul etmedi. Zorladigimda sahiplerle konusmam gerektigini ve onlarin musait olmadigini ve ne zaman musait olacaklari hakkinda hicbir fikrinin olmadigini soyledi.
Ayrilmadan once gorevliye cihazi bizzat test ettirdim. Arizali oldugunu dogruladi ama yine de iadeyi kabul etmedi.

Arizali cihazi satin aldiktan birkac saat sonra, web sitesindeki talimatlara gore web siteleri araciligiyla onlarla iletisime gectim ve uzerinden 2 hafta gecmesine ragmen hala onlardan haber alamadim.

Tavsiyemi dinle, bu yerden uzak dur. Kar marjlari en az %800, Amazon'da daha kaliteli cihazlar, daha iyi secim ve hatta daha iyi fiyatlar var.

********Sahibine Yanit************
Makbuz benim sahip oldugum ve hala makbuzum oldugu icin sorun degildi. Gorevliye gosterdim, ilgilenmedi.
Benden hicbir e-posta almadiginiza ikna olmadim ve 87,00 $'i elinizde tutabilmek icin bir incelemeye/sikayete yalan soyleyerek yanit vermek igrenc gelmiyor mu? Gercekten diyorum? Durustlugunuzun degeri 87,00 dolardan az mi?

Iceri girdim ve bu genc cocuk envanter yapiyordu. Ne yaptigini anlatti ve yardima ihtiyacim olup olmadigini sordu. Ona bilmedigim yeni bir sey olup olmadigini sordum. Gorunuse gore yeni bir seyi yoktu cunku daha once gormedigim bir seyi onermedi, bu yuzden ona yardimin icin tesekkur ederim dedim ama iyiyim, etrafima bakip istedigim herhangi bir seyi begenip begenmedigimi gorecegim satin almak. Sunu da eklemeliyim ki buranin her kosesinde kameralar var ve bana bir suru kamera verdiklerini bildirme ihtiyaci duydu. Tamam, simdi benim hirsiz falan oldugumu dusundugunu hissediyorum. Bu yuzden ona bir kez daha yardiminiz icin tesekkur ettigimi soyledim, gidip yaptiginiz ise devam edebilirsiniz. Hayir orada durup bana bakmak istedi ve bu beni gercekten rahatsiz etti. O zamanlar cebimde 4 bin dolarim vardi ve minimum 500 dolari orada harcayacaktim. Ermeni oldugum icin ve belki guzel giyindigim icin ya da bu sorunun ne oldugunu bilmedigim icin ayrimciliga ugradim ama gercekten ayrimciliga ugradigimi hissediyorum ve hangi hukuki meselelerle ilgilendigimi gorecegim. Cok duygusal bir depresyondayim, bana bu sekilde davranilmasi bana sanki evden hic cikmiyormusum gibi hissettiriyor. Saat 16:00'da bir avukatla randevum var ve umarim o seyin bunu baska birine yapmamasini saglayacak yasal islem baslatilir.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Always google the brand BEFORE You Buy. They're looking to make a quick sale, at the end of the day. Of the 5 staff members we interacted with 2 were semi-helpful. One of the others got a little too close for personal comfort.

The biggest reason for the star rating is the quality of the products. My partner and I bought roughly $300 worth of products, all together, and were disappointed with all of them.
Update: we were able to find 2 of the exact same $100 toys on Amazon for half the price (including shipping)
I question why they stock such poorly reviewed toys.

Unfortunately, I really can't recommend this shop. Though, if you need a cute corset, you'll find a variety here.

featured_reviews.response_from_owner_text:
First, there is no way you interacted with 5 staff members on any given shift, on any day.  So exaggeration for dramatic effect?  And I would appreciate knowing if any of my staff members causes distress to a customer rather than reading about it on Google.

We do not allow returns if the product has been opened,  for obvious health reasons, unless it is defective.  We will show you ANY PRODUCT in the store, if you ask us to open it.  My staff will open any product to show and demonstrate for a customer while wearing gloves to ensure everything remains sanitary.  There is signage all over the store reminding customers that we are happy to show any product they wish to see.

As for Amazon, it is a personal choice to purchase products for intimate use on a platform that cannot guarantee if a product is genuine, body safe, or if it has been previously used (think about that for a minute).

Our store prides itself on stocking a range of products to meet the wants, desires and needs of our customers.  I am disappointed that you were unhappy with your visit to our store and that you felt a one star review was warranted.  At least the corsets were acceptable.  Thank you for your review.
featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Satin Almadan ONCE daima markayi Google'da arayin. Gunun sonunda hizli bir satis yapmak istiyorlar. Etkilesimde bulundugumuz 5 personelden 2'si yari yardimciydi. Digerlerinden biri kisisel rahatligi icin biraz fazla yaklasti.

Yildiz verilmesinin en buyuk sebebi urunlerin kalitesidir. Ortagim ve ben hep birlikte yaklasik 300 $ degerinde urun satin aldik ve hepsinden hayal kirikligina ugradik.
Guncelleme: Amazon'da ayni 100 $'lik oyuncaklardan 2 tanesini yari fiyatina bulabildik (nakliye dahil)
Neden bu kadar kotu incelenmis oyuncaklari stokladiklarini sorguluyorum.

Ne yazik ki, bu dukkani gercekten tavsiye edemiyorum. Yine de sevimli bir korseye ihtiyaciniz varsa, burada bir cesit bulacaksiniz.
featured_reviews.response_from_owner_translated_text:
Oncelikle, herhangi bir gunde, herhangi bir vardiyada 5 personel ile etkilesime girmenizin hicbir yolu yoktur. Dramatik etki icin abarti mi yani? Ve personelimden herhangi birinin bir musteriyi rahatsiz edip etmedigini Google'da okumak yerine bilmekten memnuniyet duyarim.

Urun, saglik acisindan bariz nedenlerden dolayi acilmissa, kusurlu olmadigi surece iadeye izin vermiyoruz. Acmamizi isterseniz magazadaki HERHANGI BIR URUNU size gosterecegiz. Personelim, her seyin hijyenik kalmasini saglamak icin eldiven giyerek musteriye gostermek ve gostermek uzere her turlu urunu acacaktir. Magazanin her yerinde musterilere gormek istedikleri urunu gostermekten mutluluk duyacagimizi hatirlatan tabelalar bulunmaktadir.

Amazon'a gelince, bir urunun orijinal oldugunu, vucut icin guvenli oldugunu veya daha once kullanilmis olup olmadigini garanti edemeyen bir platformda ozel kullanima yonelik urunler satin almak kisisel bir tercihtir (bunu bir dakika dusunun).

Magazamiz musterilerimizin istek, arzu ve ihtiyaclarini karsilayacak genis urun yelpazesini stoklamaktan gurur duymaktadir. Magazamiza yaptiginiz ziyaretten memnun kalmamaniz ve tek yildizli bir incelemenin gerekli oldugunu dusunmeniz beni hayal kirikligina ugratti. En azindan korseler kabul edilebilirdi. Incelemeniz icin tesekkur ederiz.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Buradan alisveris yapmayin. Kusurlu bir urun satildi ve daha bir saat bile gecmeden magazayla iletisime gecip durumu bildirmek ve gelip para iadesi alip alamayacagimi ya da urunu faydalanamayacagim bir seyle degistirip degistiremeyecegimi sordugumda hala oradaydim. tam bir tartismaya donustu. Magazaya vardigimda bir tuzakti, yonetici onunla arka tarafa gelmek icin ayrilana kadar arka tarafa gitti. Magazada merhaba diyordum kusura bakmayin ne zamandan beri magazayla ilgileniyorsunuz ve kimse ilgilenmiyor o ve tum mallar denetimsiz birakilir. Sonra uc polis arabasi yaklasiyor ve ben disari cikiyorum ve onlara el sallamaya basliyorum cunku zaten hayal kirikligina ugradim ve yardima ihtiyacim var cunku magazada yardim almakta zorlaniyorum cunku yonetici her zaman kaba davraniyor. sanki kucuk cerceveli siyah kadinlara karsi bir seyleri var ve bu sadece benim kisisel gorusum orada alisveris yaparken bana hep boyle hissettiriyor ve eger magazada baska biri varsa cunku burasi civarda bir magaza oldugundan oraya cok cabuk giriyorum ve onu gormezden geliyorum cunku onun tam da boyle bir insan oldugunu dusunuyorum ama bugun berbat bir deneyimdi. Degisim icin magazadayken ve orada durup memura ne oldugunu acikladigim sirada 911'i arayarak bir soygun oldugunu soyleyerek sahte bir polis suclamasinda bulundu. sadece onemsiz ve cok saldirgandi Daha once magazada parami harcadigimda ve magazadan aldigim seylerden keyif aldigimda hirsiz muamelesi yaparak ayrimciliga ugradim Neden bu kadar zor zamanlar gecirdigimi anlamiyorum ve umarim Hic kimsenin benim yasadigim deneyimi yasamadigini ama bu korkunctu ve bir daha buraya geri donmeyecegim...

Para iadesinin tamami boyunca, bir magazaya gittiginizi ve bir urun satin aldiginizi, test etmek icin birkac pil alacaginizi ve magazayi arayarak bunun ise yaramadigini bildirecegini ve ardindan bunun yoneticiyle kucumseyici bir konusmaya donustugunu hayal edebiliyor musunuz? hararetli bir tartismaya giriyorsunuz ve magazaya, profesyonellikten yoksun ve polisin sizi soygun icin cagirdigi satis elemanindan degil, satin alma isleminizde size yardimci olan satis elemanindan yardim almaya calisirken geliyorsunuz, bu kulaga dogru geliyor mu? Musterinize kusurlu bir cihaz sattiginiz icin bu davranis tarzina benziyor. Yardim istemek icin aradigimda ve yonetici bunu yapmak istediginde birinin bana karsi magazayi soymaya geldigimi soyleyerek yalan ihbarda bulunmasinin adil oldugunu dusunmuyorum. Beni adimla cagirin ve alayci sozler soyleyin lutfen paranizi burada israf etmeyin lutfen paranizi degerli bir yere harcayin takdir edin Baska bir yonetici var mi bilmiyorum ama bugun ugrasmak zorunda kaldigim kisi o her zaman oraya gittigimde magazadayim ve o kesinlikle berbat, saclarini ayri tarzda orguler halinde takan, sisman bir Afrikali-Amerikali kadin ve kaba olmaya calismiyorum, tum sekil ve bedenler guzel, bu kadin sadece gorunuste kaba ve cirkin iceri.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Last time I was there I noticed several things that may help answer some questions.

1, the theater is closed
2, there are women that go there that give me the impression a pay as you go arrangement can be negotiated, as with most businesses of this nature
3, some women do go into the arcade, some are crossdressers.
4, they take cash and credit cards.

The place itself has gone through a turnover in staff. The new people seem nice enough but lack product knowledge, a common problem actually in most book stores/arcades.

Not much other than the basics, very little in the way of medium to high end products. When asked about anything they don't have, the canned response is to go online, translating in lost sales. Unfortunately lack of products knowledge and a minimum of curiosity prevents the clerk's from suggesting a product will have more than an intended purpose, something I have done many times to create something more suited to my needs until the industry catches up.

Movies appear to be reasonably well stocked, theater isn't anything special but provides the needed space for whatever  comes along, so long as people are discreet and use common sense. Higher volume much the same as anywhere else. All types tend to frequent the joint but most are standard rate.

All in all between the 3 stores in the area one can find something, but don't expect anything fancy in the way of fetish gear, leather, etc. I believe that every market has the potential to sella better product if the right case is made to spend a few more dollars. Thats the same in any sales environment, including adult in nature. Interesting how the management of all three of the local outlets expects far more professionalism than they seem to be able to hire.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
En son oraya gittigimde bazi sorularin yanitlanmasina yardimci olabilecek birkac sey fark ettim.

1, tiyatro kapali
2, oraya giden kadinlar var ve bana bu tur cogu iste oldugu gibi, kullandigin kadar ode duzenlemesinin muzakere edilebilecegi izlenimini veriyor
3, bazi kadinlar atari salonuna giriyor, bazilari ise crossdresser.
4, nakit para ve kredi karti aliyorlar.

Mekanin kendisi personel degisiminden gecti. Yeni insanlar yeterince iyi gorunuyorlar ancak urun bilgisinden yoksunlar, bu aslinda cogu kitapcida/oyuncuda yaygin bir sorun.

Temel urunler disinda pek bir sey yok, orta ve ust duzey urunler acisindan cok az sey var. Ellerinde olmayan herhangi bir sey soruldugunda, hazir cevap internete girmek ve bu da satis kaybi anlamina geliyor. Ne yazik ki urun bilgisi eksikligi ve asgari duzeyde merak, tezgahtarin bir urunun amaclanan amactan daha fazlasina sahip olacagini one surmesini engelliyor; bu, endustri yetisene kadar ihtiyaclarima daha uygun bir sey yaratmak icin bircok kez yaptigim bir sey.

Filmler oldukca iyi stoklanmis gibi gorunuyor, tiyatro ozel bir sey degil ama insanlar sagduyulu olduklari ve sagduyularini kullandiklari surece onlerine cikan her sey icin gerekli alani sagliyor. Daha yuksek ses seviyesi, diger yerlerdekiyle hemen hemen aynidir. Tum turler eklemi sik sik kullanma egilimindedir ancak cogu standart orandir.

Sonucta bolgedeki 3 magaza arasinda bir seyler bulabilirsiniz, ancak fetis kiyafetleri, deri vb. gibi gosterisli hicbir sey beklemeyin. Her pazarin, eger dogru kasa bulunursa, daha iyi bir urun satma potansiyeline sahip olduguna inaniyorum. birkac dolar daha harcamak icin yapildi. Yetiskinlere yonelik olanlar da dahil olmak uzere tum satis ortamlarinda durum aynidir. Yerel satis noktalarinin ucunun de yonetiminin, ise alabileceklerinden cok daha fazla profesyonellik beklemesi ilginc.

featured_reviews.review_id: I've been to adult bookstores all throughout the bay area and most of them are well kept, with polite staff, and an attempt to create a discreet, if not a tad tawdry ambience.  That is what the customer expects when he plunks down his 10 bucks to wander into the wanton for a while. While traveling through Fairfield I happened upon Secrets next to Travis Airforcebase so decided to venture in. I had been there before and had some great times what with the proximity to the air force base and the fresh meat that that entails. But alas on a Sunday evening it was quite dead and in the final 30 minutes of my "shift" there, the janitor completely took over the facility opening the back doors, which flooded the arcade with light as he loudly and quite obnoxiously cleaned all of the stalls. Now I understand the importance of clealiness, but this establishment should really work on a schedule that enables the janitor to do his duties without destroying the ambience that customers pay for. This guy was loudly grunting the whole time he was cleaning, was making bizarre noises in the bathroom and basically treating the place like there wasn't paying customers in attendance. Once he was finally done, I went to the front desk to explain my dissatisfaction and the fact that 30 minutes of the hour I paid for was completely disrupted and not what I had paid for. Taylor at the front desk was not sympathetic, rudely refused to offer any solace as to his inability to provide the paying guest with the dark arcade we've come to expect. This Secrets with their 1 hour time slots should get with the better business model perfected by awesome places like the El Cerrito Secrets which is always extremely busy. You pay the same amount but can stay for 4 to 5 hours and there isn't staff all up in your business, looking to tell you time is up, or loudly and creepily sanitizing the place . Places like Steamworks does the requisite cleaning in the least disturbing manner, you barely notice they are present. My request would be for the manager to refund me my money or provide a discounted admission in the future since they were unable to provide what I was paying for. And if this place would only think outside the box and takes it's cues from some far more successful busy adult establishments, with their adjacent military neighbor, they could be far more profitable.  And better training the staff would be helpful as well.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Korfez bolgesindeki yetiskin kitapcilarina gittim ve cogu bakimli, kibar personelli ve biraz bayagi bir ortam olmasa da sagduyulu bir ortam yaratma cabasiyla. Musterinin, bir sureligine ahlaksizligin icinde dolasmak icin 10 dolarini dusurdugu zaman bekledigi sey budur. Fairfield'da seyahat ederken Travis Hava Kuvvetleri Ussu'nun yanindaki Secrets'a rastladim ve iceri girmeye karar verdim. Daha once oradaydim ve hava kuvvetleri ussune yakinligi ve bunun gerektirdigi taze et nedeniyle harika zamanlar gecirdim. Ama ne yazik ki bir Pazar aksami tamamen olmustu ve oradaki "vardiyam"in son 30 dakikasinda, kapici arka kapilari acarak tesisin yonetimini tamamen ele gecirdi ve yuksek sesle ve oldukca igrenc bir sekilde tum binayi temizlerken pasaji isikla doldurdu. tezgahlar. Artik temizligin onemini anliyorum, ancak bu kurulusun gercekten de kapicinin, musterilerin para odedigi ortami bozmadan gorevlerini yapmasina olanak taniyan bir program uzerinde calismasi gerekiyor. Bu adam temizlik yaptigi sure boyunca yuksek sesle homurdaniyor, banyoda tuhaf sesler cikariyor ve sanki para odeyen musteriler yokmus gibi davraniyordu. Nihayet isi bittiginde, memnuniyetsizligimi ve odedigim saatin 30 dakikasinin tamamen kesintiye ugradigini ve odedigim ucretin olmadigini aciklamak icin on buroya gittim. On burodaki Taylor anlayisli degildi, odeme yapan konuklara bekledigimiz karanlik pasaji saglayamamasi konusunda herhangi bir teselli sunmayi kaba bir sekilde reddetti. 1 saatlik zaman araliklariyla bu Sirlar, her zaman son derece mesgul olan El Cerrito Sirlari gibi harika yerler tarafindan mukemmellestirilen daha iyi bir is modeliyle birlikte kullanilmalidir. Ayni tutari odersiniz ancak 4 ila 5 saat kalabilirsiniz ve isinizde size zamanin doldugunu soyleyen veya yuksek sesle ve urkutucu bir sekilde mekani dezenfekte eden personel yoktur. Steamworks gibi yerler gerekli temizligi en az rahatsiz edici sekilde yapar, onlarin varligini zar zor fark edersiniz. Istegim, yoneticinin bana parami iade etmesi veya odedigim ucreti saglayamadiklari icin gelecekte indirimli giris hakki saglamasi olacaktir. Ve eger bu yer sadece kaliplarin disinda dusunse ve ipuclarini komsu askeri komsulariyla birlikte cok daha basarili, mesgul yetiskin kuruluslarindan alirsa, cok daha karli olabilirler. Personelin daha iyi egitilmesi de yararli olacaktir.

Christi,
"Kotu bir deneyim" yasadigin icin uzgunum, yorgundun ve her seyin asiri pahali oldugunu hissettin.

Sohbetimizin oldukca hos oldugunu hissettik. Aslinda, size 1'e 1 musteri hizmeti sunmak icin neredeyse yarim saat harcadik ve musteri hizmetlerimiz bizim gurur duydugumuz seydir. Ihtiyaclarinizi, kisisel yakinlik gecmisinizi dinledik ve bu bilgilerden yola cikarak profesyonel onerilerde bulunduk; buradaki asil isimiz bu.

Hatirladigimiz kadariyla, ihtiyaclariniza ve butcenize uygun mahremiyet urunleri bulmayi defalarca denediniz, ancak bu sizin icin zorlayici oldu.

Bu nedenle, yine Ooh La La'ya yaptiginiz ziyarette size 10,00 $ fiyat araliginizda oldugumuzu gosteren tam bir kayganlastirici ve kisisel masaj yelpazesini gosterdik ve aciklamak icin zaman ayirdik. Ek olarak, mevcut mahremiyet ogelerinizi, su anda sahip oldugunuz ve artik ise yaramadigini bildirdiginiz ogeleri kullanmanin yollari hakkinda beyin firtinasi yapmaniza yardimci olduk. Size herhangi bir sey satmaya calismadik. Baska yerden satin aldiginiz seyleri duzeltmenize yardimci olmaya calistik cunku musterilerimize oncelik veriyoruz.

Son satin aliminiz acisindan mukemmel bir urun olan Shunga masaj mumunu tercih edin. Lutfen bunun, onerdigimiz diger ogeler yerine sectiginiz bir oge oldugunu unutmayin. Aslinda bir masaj mumu olan "tealight" aslinda kisisel bir tercihti. Lutfen urunu talimatlara uygun sekilde kullanmaya zaman ayirin cunku harikadir. Urun ne kadar sasirtici olsa da, ziyaretiniz sirasinda tartistiginiz boslugu doldurmayacaktir, cunku masaj yagi mumlari/tealight'lari sihirli bir sekilde tibbi sinif silikon, sarj edilebilir, hipoalerjenik, kendi kendini yaglayan kisisel masaj cihazlarina donusemez. Size tum bu kutulari isaretleyen ve 50 dolarin altindaki urunleri gosterdik.

Her neyse, uzun bir gun gecirip yoruldugunuz icin uzgunum. Umarim gelecekte daha dinlenmis oldugunuzda aradiginizi bulursunuz.

Tesekkur ederim!


BU INCELEMEYI BIZE GOSTERIN VE %10 TASARRUF EDIN!!!!!!

featured_reviews.review_id: Unfortunately my experience went from great to horrible when I realized I was quoted the wrong price. When I called to talk to the manager I quickly realized that there's no point explaining what happened (the manager immediately became argumentative) because their no return policy also means they refuse to do anything not even a minor discount or store credit. So beware before you go into this store and spend over $400 dollars on merchandise. They do not care about their customers. You might as well buy online and get cheaper prices. Also if you are disabled with a visual impairment ask someone to go with you so you get an accurate price quote on the items you want to purchase. Honest mistakes happen. The woman helping me was great but we had one miscommunication that ended up with me losing money and not satisfied with my experience. Unfortunately, I have to go back and use two punchcards worth of discounts I got from my visit. I would have preferred to use them on the misquoted item instead. After that I will go back to shopping online. Supporting local businesses just isn't worth it anymore if there's no personal touch and any mistake lands on the customer's shoulders.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Ne yazik ki, bana yanlis fiyat teklif edildigini fark ettigimde deneyimim mukemmelden korkunc bir hal aldi. Yoneticiyle konusmak icin aradigimda, olanlari aciklamanin hicbir anlami olmadigini hemen fark ettim (yonetici hemen tartismaya basladi), cunku iade etmeme politikasi ayni zamanda kucuk bir indirim veya magaza kredisi dahil hicbir seyi yapmayi reddettikleri anlamina da geliyor. Bu magazaya girmeden ve urunlere 400 dolardan fazla harcamadan once dikkatli olun. Musterilerini umursamiyorlar. Internet uzerinden de satin alabilir ve daha uygun fiyatlara sahip olabilirsiniz. Ayrica gorme engelli bir kisiyseniz, satin almak istediginiz urunler icin dogru bir fiyat teklifi alabilmeniz icin birinden sizinle gelmesini isteyin. Durust hatalar olur. Bana yardim eden kadin harikaydi ama para kaybetmeme ve deneyimimden memnun kalmama neden olan bir yanlis iletisim yasadik. Ne yazik ki geri donup ziyaretimden aldigim iki kart degerinde indirimi kullanmam gerekiyor. Bunun yerine yanlis alintilanan ogede bunlari kullanmayi tercih ederdim. Bundan sonra internetten alisverise geri donecegim. Kisisel bir dokunus yoksa ve herhangi bir hata musterinin omuzlarina yukleniyorsa, yerel isletmeleri desteklemenin artik buna degmez.

This place is amazing because of the location, a wide selection, and staff that's very friendly and knowledgeable.  Located in the heart of downtown Palm Springs with parking in front and the back making it very accessible for that quick in and out or the longer shopping trip.

Upon arriving, you will be greeted by the staff, making you feel welcome. Nikki, the manager , and Liz both were perfect in helping me decide on the toys and things that would be the fit for me.

Make sure you go check this place out. Their prices are very competitive if not lower than other places I have been, and this is a store you would be crazy not to check out. Ask for Liz, and you will be glad you did.

featured_reviews.review_id:
Great store and great customer service!!
The young lady cashier on Saturday October 16th exemplified superior customer service. Most stores have a no return policy which I totally get. I got a pair of underwear for a date. As with any undies you can't try them on, and buying and sizing is a game of luck!

Well I bought them, as they can sometimes cost a pretty penny and my luck they were too big. So I go back not 30 minutes later I explained to the clerk I just bought them and they were to big. She understood and with grace said we have a no return policy. I explained I just simply took them out of the box and she empathized as I almost started to cry. She examined the pair and said what do you need? I  a simply said a smaller size and she said "we can make it work". She was polite as when I bought them and made the whole experience pleasurable! I had this problem before at a different store and the difference in service was polar opposite (Circus of Books in Weho) like war and peace! This here is how customers should be treated!

This is a top notch store and has earned a lifetime customer because of her willingness to help. I'm gonna go back and buy two more! Treat your customers well and I'll tell everyone I know to go to this store top-notch service, gets top-notch customers. Thank you for representing this store in a great way. You're lucky to have her! Give her a raise!!

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Harika bir magaza ve harika musteri hizmetleri!!
16 Ekim Cumartesi gunu genc bayan kasiyer ustun musteri hizmetinin bir ornegini sergiledi. Cogu magazanin tamamen aldigim bir iade politikasi yoktur. Bir randevu icin bir cift ic camasiri aldim. Tum ic camasirlarinda oldugu gibi bunlari deneyemezsiniz ve satin almak ve beden olcusunu almak bir sans oyunudur!

Bazen oldukca pahaliya mal olabildikleri ve sansima cok buyuk olduklari icin onlari satin aldim. Bu yuzden 30 dakika sonra geri dondum. Gorevliye onlari yeni aldigimi ve cok buyuk olduklarini anlattim. Anladi ve nezaketle iade politikamizin olmadigini soyledi. Onlari sadece kutudan cikardigimi ve neredeyse aglamaya basladigimda empati yaptigini acikladim. Cifti inceledi ve neye ihtiyacin var dedi? Ben sadece daha kucuk bir boyut dedim ve o da "bunu calistirabiliriz" dedi. Onlari satin aldigim zamanki gibi kibardi ve tum deneyimi zevkli hale getirdi! Bu sorunu daha once farkli bir magazada yasadim ve hizmet farki savas ve baris gibi zit kutuplardaydi (Weho'daki Kitaplar Sirki)! Iste musterilere nasil davranilmasi gerektigi!

Burasi birinci sinif bir magaza ve yardim etme istegi nedeniyle omur boyu bir musteri kazandi. Geri donup iki tane daha alacagim! Musterilerinize iyi davranin, ben de tanidigim herkese bu magazaya gitmelerini, birinci sinif hizmet vermelerini, birinci sinif musteriler kazanmalarini soyleyecegim. Bu magazayi harika bir sekilde temsil ettiginiz icin tesekkur ederiz. Ona sahip oldugun icin sanslisin! Ona zam ver!!

Great management. Much better than adult store on Ming. Excellent customer service. Great product knowledge. 10/10

I bought a $300 item online, but it didn't come with maintenance items. So I start making calls.

First, I called the adult store on Ming:
Girl answers. I tell her I'm looking for two products and would like to know if she carries them. She puts me on hold for at least 10 minutes, but does check in so I know she didn't forget. Someone else picks up, and after confirming that she has the products, she refuses to have them ready at the counter to make it a quick trip (I'd like to not be seen at an adult store like many of you). Her attitude sounded like she was too good for her own shoes.

Frustrated at the thought of digging through sexual products (that others have touched on Ming Ave. eww!) to figure out the right one, I call Fun Zone on Stine:

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Harika yonetim. Ming'deki yetiskin magazasindan cok daha iyi. Mukemmel musteri hizmeti. Mukemmel urun bilgisi. 10/10

Uzun versiyon
Internetten 300 dolarlik bir urun satin aldim, ancak bakim malzemeleriyle birlikte gelmedi. Boylece arama yapmaya basliyorum.

Ilk once Ming'deki yetiskin magazasini aradim:
Kiz cevap veriyor. Ona iki urun aradigimi ve bunlari tasiyip tasimadigini ogrenmek istedigimi soyledim. Beni en az 10 dakika bekletiyor ama unutmadigini bilmem icin kontrol ediyor. Baska biri telefonu aliyor ve urunlerin kendisinde oldugunu dogruladiktan sonra, hizli bir yolculuk olsun diye onlari tezgahta hazir bulundurmayi reddediyor (cogunuz gibi ben de yetiskinlere yonelik bir magazada gorulmek istemiyorum). Tutumu sanki kendi ayakkabilari icin fazla iyiymis gibi geliyordu.

Dogru olani bulmak icin cinsel urunleri (digerlerinin de Ming Ave. eww'e degindigi) arastirma fikrinden bikarak Stine'daki Eglence Bolgesi'ni aradim:
Aradigima memnun olmus gibi gorunen ve yuzume bir gulumseme koymaya devam eden neseli bir yonetici tarafindan karsilandim. Ilk olarak bana 30 dolar kazandiran tavsiyeler veriyor. Artik bu magazanin harika insanlara sahip oldugunu biliyorum. Ihtiyacim olan diger malzemeleri acikladiktan sonra, lutfen guclu bir marka secip bunlari kasada bulundurur mu diye sordum, boylece oraya gidip odeme yapabilirim. O da kabul ediyor ve soz verdigim gibi geldigimde onlari hazirliyor. Iki genc kadin olan calisanlari da ayni derecede arkadas canlisi ve bilgiliydi. Genel olarak, bana bu sekilde iyi davranilmasi hosuma gidiyor ve bu magazayi harika, hizli ve gizli bir musteri deneyiminden hoslanan herkese kesinlikle tavsiye edecegim. Tanriya sukur ki bu kasabada hala nasil ise alinacagini bilen biri var! Yine 10/10
